Gary is QPC’s Director of Product Management and creates the product strategy and roadmap for the QPC group. Gary is a seasoned contact centre, customer experience and analytics executive who is passionate about both customer and people experience, and using better data to make better decisions. Gary holds a degree in Maths & Statistics as well as MBA in Finance, he is also a fellow of the Operations Research Society.



