Author Information
GARY SMITH is a full-time home-based trader and the author of Live
the Dream by Profitably Day Trading, which has been hailed as the
best day trading book ever written. Gary has been profiled in
Futures and Technical Analysis of Stocks & Commodities and is a
frequent speaker at trading seminars.


